WEBVTT

00:00:28.493 --> 00:00:30.442
pensant que podia simplement eliminar-lo.

00:00:30.442 --> 00:00:32.111
O podia fer el que tots



00:00:33.371 --> 00:00:34.821
sempre hem volgut fer.

00:00:34.851 --> 00:00:37.622
(Rialles)

00:00:38.431 --> 00:00:40.880
I li vaig dir, "Solomon, 
el teu correu m'intriga."

00:00:40.880 --> 00:00:43.476
(Rialles)

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:48.476
(Aplaudiments)

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:50.920
I el joc ja havia començat!

00:00:52.854 --> 00:00:54.874
Ell va respondre, 
"Benvolgut James Veitch,

00:00:54.874 --> 00:00:56.199
t'enviarem or."

00:00:56.199 --> 00:00:57.896
(Rialles)

00:00:58.302 --> 00:01:01.199
"Guanyaràs el 10% 
de tot l'or que reparteixis"